    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[ContentData], [c].[CreaDate], [c].[CreaUser], [c].[DocVideoDesc], [c].[DocumentType], [c].[IsActive], [c].[IsDeleted], [c].[IsState], [c].[IsStatus], [c].[ModDate], [c].[ModUser], [c].[OrderNo], [c].[ResponseType], [c].[SectionId], [c].[VideoLink]
    FROM [Content] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t] ON [a].[ContentID] = [t].[Id]
WHERE [a].[IsDeleted] IS NULL"

FROM (
    SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[CreaDate], [s].[CreaUser], [s].[Definition], [s].[IsActive], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[IsState], [s].[IsStatus], [s].[ModDate], [s].[ModUser], [s].[Name], [s].[OrderNo], [s].[WorkshopId]

FROM [ActionData] AS [a]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[ContentData], [c].[CreaDate], [c].[CreaUser], [c].[DocVideoDesc], [c].[DocumentType], [c].[IsActive], [c].[IsDeleted], [c].[IsState], [c].[IsStatus], [c].[ModDate], [c].[ModUser], [c].[OrderNo], [c].[ResponseType], [c].[SectionId], [c].[VideoLink]
